    <title>安利!</title>
    <link href="http://chzpmax.piercebrands.top/2017/11/03/anli/"/>
    <id>http://chzpmax.piercebrands.top/2017/11/03/anli/</id>
    <published>2017-11-03T02:10:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-11-03T04:31:09.852Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>怎么给你<s>儿子</s>好朋友安利游戏呢？</p><p>总归还是要写点代码的，其实这是很早期的代码特别Lowb，翻东西看到挺有意思的就拿出来好了。</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h1 id="普通安利"><a href="#普通安利" class="headerlink" title="普通安利"></a>普通安利</h1><p>比如找一堆资料，直接拍脸上，给他看这游戏各种牛逼的操作，牛逼的画面，牛逼的游戏性，各种截图，文字描述，安利到他必须去看。或者旁敲侧击的说最近又一款巨好玩的游戏… 对了你不是喜欢玩xxx么，我看到一款…</p><blockquote><p>当上述说的都没有用的时候！那你只能自！己！做！个！（滑稽）</p></blockquote><h1 id="游戏"><a href="#游戏" class="headerlink" title="游戏"></a>游戏</h1><p>巨大的挑战！安利什么呢？当然是巨牛逼的DOTA！</p><h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><p>首先，妮要收集一些素材吧，比如一些看起来特别亲切的图片，给他特别友好的第一印象，最好让他看到就说，卧槽，太牛逼了。</p><p><img src="/images/a3/a3_p1.jpg" alt=""></p><p>比如上面这张图片就很好的表达了效果，当然说完牛逼之后，他会不会<s>打你一顿</s>跟你握手？表达谢意。就不知道了。</p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>代码不是重要的，最主要的时通过一些友好的提示，词语让他感受到你的诚意！比如下面这几种。</p><p>非常简单！只用一些对话框，就可以搞定，（当然我这个写的就非常lowb了）</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">dotarun</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> textcon = <span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">'textcon'</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> textw = textcon.innerHTML;</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//alert(textcon.innerHTML);</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> choosehero =  prompt(<span class="string">"选择妮的英雄！"</span>,<span class="string">"火枪手！"</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (choosehero==<span class="string">"火枪手！"</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"儿子眼光不错啊！"</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//document.write("儿子眼光不错啊！");</span></div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"儿子眼光不错啊！"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"儿子选择了火枪手！"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//document.write("&lt;br&gt;");</span></div><div class="line">herotext();</div><div class="line">choose();</div><div class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"除了火枪还想玩别的英雄？！吃翔去吧！"</span>);</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"除了火枪还想玩别的英雄？！吃翔去吧！"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"儿子选择了火枪手！"</span>);</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"儿子选择了火枪手！"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">herotext();</div><div class="line">choose();</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"未完待续..."</span>);</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"未完待续..."</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">choose</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"来帮爹随便挑个英雄吧！"</span>);</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"来帮爹随便挑个英雄吧！"</span>;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> choosehero2 = confirm(<span class="string">"是否为爹选择屠夫？"</span>);</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (choosehero2==<span class="literal">true</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"可以的儿子，很懂爹"</span>);</div><div class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"小赤佬的，造反啦！爹就要玩屠夫！"</span>);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>;</div><div class="line">alert(<span class="string">"儿子帮爹选择了屠夫！"</span>);</div><div class="line">textcon.innerHTML=textcon.innerHTML+<span class="string">"儿子帮爹选择了屠夫！"</span>;</div><div class="line">herotext2();</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>来解释一下，这段代码主要体现出了，给他选择一个非常<s>弱鸡</s>强力的英雄，<s>不要也不行！</s>就非常友好，肯定会让他非常兴奋！然后再给自己选择一个特别<s>强力</s>让他来吊打你，再通过一些友好的提示框仿佛在跟他沟通一样，让他沉浸进去，就特别高级了。</p><h2 id="页面"><a href="#页面" class="headerlink" title="页面"></a>页面</h2><p>这里就不多说了，放几张图，满满的诚意扑面而来？!</p><p><img src="/images/a3/a3_p2.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="/images/a3/a3_p3.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="/images/a3/a3_p5.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="/images/a3/a3_p4.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="/images/a3/a3_p6.png" alt=""></p><p>结果不用说，自然是成功…….了？</p><h1 id="结束"><a href="#结束" class="headerlink" title="结束"></a>结束</h1><p>其实是一朋友提醒到我了，然后想试试代码片段怎么展示的。就胡逼搞了这么一篇（滑稽）</p><p>最后还是真-安利一个网站，听听电台特别好。什么类型节目都有，当然主要是游戏，但不止于游戏吧。像“牛逼疯了，巨傻逼”，这种生动的词汇就是从里面学来的（一本正经）。</p><p>机核网：<a href="https://www.g-cores.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://www.g-cores.com/</a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;怎么给你&lt;s&gt;儿子&lt;/s&gt;好朋友安利游戏呢？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;总归还是要写点代码的，其实这是很早期的代码特别Lowb，翻东西看到挺有意思的就拿出来好了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
